    <H2 class="max-w-4xl">Your website is not just a digital brochure,&nbsp;<span class="text-blue-500">it’s your most critical tool.</span></H2>
    <div class="flex sm:flex-row flex-col gap-4 mt-16">
        <ButtonLink href="#">Start Now</ButtonLink>
    </div>
